OL,3,CBrighton Museum to close for essential
OL,4,Croof repairs
OL,6,FBrighton Museum will be closing from
OL,7,Ftoday (Monday 5 August) so that
OL,8,Fessential roof repairs can be carried
OL,9,Fout to the Grade II listed building.
OL,11,FThe museum and art gallery will be
OL,12,Fclosed until Thursday 12 September
OL,13,Fwhilst contractors repair the 220-year-
OL,14,Fold roof to bring the building up to
OL,15,F21st century requirements.
OL,17,FA structural survey in 2019 found the
OL,18,Fbuilding, one of the first purpose-
OL,19,Fbuilt museums in the UK, needs urgent
OL,20,Frepairs.
