OL,3,CBrighton Museum to close for essential
OL,4,Croof repairs
OL,6,FThe work will be funded by a grant of
OL,7,F#1,463,769 by the Department for
OL,8,FDigital, Culture, Media & Sport via
OL,9,FArts Council England.
OL,11,FBrighton & Hove City Council who own
OL,12,Fthe Royal Pavilion which is managed by
OL,13,FBrighton & Hove Museums have provided
OL,14,Fa grant of #500k for the work.
OL,16,FCEO of Brighton & Hove Museums, Hedley
OL,17,FSwain, said: "We're sorry the museum
OL,18,Fwill close during this period as we
OL,19,Fknow visitors will be disappointed.
