OL,3,CBrighton Museum to close for essential
OL,4,Croof repairs
OL,6,F"The work on the roof is essential to
OL,7,Fprotect visitors and staff, our
OL,8,Fcollections and the building.
OL,10,F"It needs to be carried out at a time
OL,11,Fwhen the weather is expected to be
OL,12,Fdry, to reduce the risk of water
OL,13,Fdamage while the work is being done.
OL,15,F"The summer months are the best time
OL,16,Fto conduct this work and will mean the
OL,17,Fclosure time will be shorter.
